title: Ta-Bitjet
extract: Ta-Bitjet is an ancient goddess of Egyptian mythology. She is identified as the consort of Haroeris. Ta-Bitjet is a scorpion goddess and the blood that flowed from when Horus/Haroeris ruptured her hymen can serve as a panacea for all poisons. She could be associated with another bride of one of the Horuses, Serket.
